events.name: Inaugural Jaipur GDG Cloud Meetup + GDG DevFest 2019
events.description:
We're pleased to welcome you to the inaugural GDG Cloud meetup in the pink city of Jaipur! We're collaborating with the GDG Jaipur meetup group to bring the DevFest 2019 to you.

We look forward to hosting you for a day of fun, learning and collaboration!

The final agenda for this event is

10:00 - 10:30 AM Doors Open, Registrations
10:30 AM - 11:00 AM Introduction to MTX & GDG Cloud Jaipur
11:00 AM - 11:45 PM Interpretable Machine Learning (Sayak Paul)
11:45 AM - 12:30 PM Demystifying TensorFlow (Gaurav Kheterpal)
12:30 PM - 1:30 PM Lunch and Networking
1:30 PM - 2:00 PM Fun Quiz
2:00 PM- 2:45 PM BlockChain and Cryptocurrency (Susmit)
2:45 PM - 3:15 PM Fun Activity
3:14 PM - 4:15 PM PyTorch, TensorFlow, Deep Learning (Sabyasachi Mukhopadhyay)
4:15 PM - 4:45 PM Wrap Up, Swag Distribution

group_profile.intro: BITS Pilani & MIT Alumni, Nearly two decades of Industry experience, currently working as Chief Technology Officer at MTX Group, Google Enthusiast, Salesforce MVP, developer at heart!
